deals.title: Build Your Own Indian Quesadillas
deals.itemDescription:
Quesadilla is a golden crescent, a folded embrace of warmth and flavor. It begins with the simple elegance of a flour tortilla. As it sizzles, the tortilla's edges become burnished and crisp, while its center softens to a supple perfection. 
Inside, a cascade of cheese, melts into a molten, amber sea, holding all other ingredients in a gooey suspension. Into this warm embrace, a bounty of flavors is tucked.

deals.title: Build Your Own Indian Burrito
deals.itemDescription:
" A burrito is a compact universe of flavor, a handheld epic of textures and tastes. It is a humble cylinder of sustenance, swaddled tightly in its soft, warm flour tortilla like a precious newborn. 
Before the first bite, the burrito is a study in potential. Through its foil sheath, a whisper of warmth suggests the rich, molten core within. Unwrapped, it presents a canvas of simple, elegant geometry—a flawless, rolled form that promises a journey in every mouthful. "
